

# Sublime Ctags package


## Setup

1. First Install

2. Go to directory in Terminal and type the following command:

	ctags -R -f .tags



## Commands

navigate_to_definition ctrl+t ctrl+t or ctrl+alt+]

jump_back ctrl+t ctrl+b or ctrl+alt+[

jump_back to_last_modification ctrl+t ctrl+m

  ==============================  ================  ===========  ======================
  Command                         Key Binding       Alt Binding  Mouse Binding
  ==============================  ================  ===========  ======================
  rebuild_ctags                   ctrl+t, ctrl+r
  navigate_to_definition          ctrl+t, ctrl+t    ctrl+>       ctrl+shift+left_click
  jump_prev                       ctrl+t, ctrl+b    ctrl+<       ctrl+shift+right_click
  show_symbols                    alt+s
  show_symbols (all files)        alt+shift+s
  show_symbols (suffix)           ctrl+alt+shift+s
  ==============================  ================  ===========  ======================